name: Core_FileAccessMode
description: An enumeration of file access modes.@(newline())
The enumeration elements can be combined.

elements.name: Core_FileAccessMode_Read
elements.description: Read access. Can be combined with @{code('Core_FileAccessMode_Write')}.

elements.name: Core_FileAccessMode_Write
elements.description: Write access. Can be combined with @{code('Core_FileAccessMode_Read')}.

elements.name: Core_FileAccessMode_ReadWrite
elements.description: Read and write access. Alias for @{code('Core_FileAccessMode_Read|Core_FileAccessMode_Write')} and for @{code('Core_FileAccessMode_WriteRead')}.

elements.name: Core_FileAccessMode_WriteRead
elements.description: Write and read access. Alias for @{code('Core_FileAccessMode_Write|Core_FileAccessMode_Read')} and for @{code('Core_FileAccessMode_ReadWrite')}.
